channel.title: What is session time out?
channel.description: Well i was posting something, and when i clicked post i got the message Session time out and some other things i dont remember. What does this mean. I also have this on my own forums wich im making atm. Can someone please help me? Also i have very slow download speeds, but that has nothing to do with this site but i think it has the same cause.

item.title: What is session time out?
item.dc:creator: @archerer98 Archer
item.description:

when you post something,then go to post something else,if you post something else in 20 seconds or less it makes you wait before you post again
